==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: bonehead
<hw>bone"head`</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a person of low intelligence; a
dunce; a blockhead; -- used deprecatingly to express a low opinion of
someone's intelligence or capabilities.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> dunce, dunderhead, numskull, blockhead, lunkhead,
hammerhead, knucklehead, loggerhead, muttonhead, shithead,
fuckhead.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>boneheaded</ent>⟦br⟧
